strings: <voice_0x01000B0B><se_high>Accuracy: That was how we met. But where is the laughter, joy and tears?
<voice_0x01000B0C><se_low>January: My work is not done yet!
<voice_0x01000B0D><se_low>January: Here are the best ones! I am not going to tell you how this man saved me....
<voice_0x01000B0F><se_low>January: You probably know that birds read history, too. Which we read, chief
<voice_0x01000B10><se_low>January: But not the skin of the nose.
